data.description: Don't miss this investor's special! Located in the heart of downtown Ames, it boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a unique charm. The property features an enclosed front porch, perfect for awaiting trick-or-treaters and a spacious detached two-car garage with additional storage space to store your headless horseman. Inside, the original hardwood floors are dying to be refinished. While it may have a spooky theme, this large house offers plenty of potential and is worth a closer look. Don't let Michael Myers scare you away!
